{"data":[{"date":"Th\u1ee9 B\u1ea3y, ng\u00e0y 24/03/2018 04:51 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: Ibra \u0111\u1ed5i s\u1ed1 \u00e1o, CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C gia nh\u1eadp \u201c\u0111\u1ea1i gia n\u01b0\u1edbc M\u1ef9\u201d","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-09/thumbnail/960-1520600242-943-width640height480.jpg","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-947329\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-947329\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Chia tay MU, Ibra CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C l\u1ed9 \u201cb\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi\u201d trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau khi n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay <strong>MU</strong>, c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt gi\u1edd, Zlatan Ibrahimovic \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi c\u00f3 ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a anh v\u1edbi LA Galaxy \u2013 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1eafm ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ee7a t\u1eeb gi\u1ea3i Nh\u00e0 ngh\u1ec1 M\u1ef9 (MLS).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf c\u1edd hoa, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u1ea3nh b\u00eca trang ch\u1ee7 Twitter c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh Ibra m\u1eb7c \u00e1o tr\u1eafng truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a CLB n\u00e0y. LA Galaxy c\u0169ng t\u1eebng l\u00e0 n\u01a1i \u201cd\u01b0\u1ee1ng gi\u00e0\u201d c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i <em>MU</em> kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 David Beckham.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: Ibra \u0111\u1ed5i s\u1ed1 \u00e1o, CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C gia nh\u1eadp \u201c\u0111\u1ea1i gia n\u01b0\u1edbc M\u1ef9\u201d - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-24/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-Ibra-doi-so-ao-CHiNH-THuC-gia-nhap-dai-gia-nuoc-My-dy_sm5lvaaaphd0-1521833682-715-width660height990.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Ibrahimovic \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay MU \u0111\u1ec3 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o LA Galaxy</p>\r\n\r\n<p>T\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi, Ibra s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 nh\u01b0 s\u1ed1 \u00e1o g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t anh m\u1eb7c \u1edf <u>MU</u> m\u00e0 \u201cl\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng\u201d 36 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n s\u1ebd m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 9.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>V\u00ec Neymar, \u201cQu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\u201d s\u1ebd \u0111em Pogba \u201ct\u1ebf th\u1ea7n\u201d v\u00e0 h\u1ee9a tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng \u201ckh\u1ee7ng\u201d</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nh\u1eadt b\u00e1o th\u1ec3 thao T\u00e2y Ban Nha Diario Gol m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y cho hay, MU \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh qua m\u1eb7t Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh \u2013 Neymar.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 mong c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u201cTi\u1ec3u Pele\u201d trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Man \u0111\u1ecf s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3 cho PSG 260 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 Paul Pogba \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed \u0111\u1ec3 trao \u0111\u1ed5i. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, MU c\u00f2n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 35 tri\u1ec7u euro m\u1ed7i n\u0103m cho Neymar n\u1ebfu anh ch\u1ecbu gia nh\u1eadp \u201cNh\u00e0 h\u00e1t c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1\u201d.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Real ch\u1edd Rashford s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh th\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ronaldo</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Trong n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi 2018/19, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn Marcus Rashford (MU). Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u1edbi 20 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf \u201cQu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\u201d m\u00f9a n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u201cK\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng\u201d Real hy v\u1ecdng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gia nh\u1eadp s\u00e2n Bernabeu theo b\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u2013 Cristiano Ronaldo.</p><p></p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><div style=\"text-align: center;width: 100%;clear: both;position: relative;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"position:relative;max-width: 660px;margin: 0 auto\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: Ibra \u0111\u1ed5i s\u1ed1 \u00e1o, CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C gia nh\u1eadp \u201c\u0111\u1ea1i gia n\u01b0\u1edbc M\u1ef9\u201d - 2\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-24/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-Ibra-doi-so-ao-CHiNH-THuC-gia-nhap-dai-gia-nuoc-My-rashford_-_ronaldo_-_mu_-_real1510798064-1521833682-818-width660height439.jpg\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"24h-banner-in-image\" style=\"position: absolute;display: block;overflow: hidden;width: 660px;height: 90px;color: white;bottom: 0px;left: 0px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"24h-banner-in-image-close\" style=\"top:5px;right: 5px;position: absolute;display: none;overflow: hidden;width: 22px;height: 22px;color: #ccc;font-size: large;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: Ibra \u0111\u1ed5i s\u1ed1 \u00e1o, CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C gia nh\u1eadp \u201c\u0111\u1ea1i gia n\u01b0\u1edbc M\u1ef9\u201d - 3\" onclick=\"in_image_close();\" id=\"in-image-close\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/24h_banner_image_library/in-image-close.svg\"></img>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n                \r\n            </div></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Rashford coi Ronaldo l\u00e0 th\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1eddi m\u00ecnh</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Quy\u1ebft c\u00f9ng Chelsea ph\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1m th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ed5i sao Real \u2013 Bayern</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Theo t\u1edd Don Balon (T\u00e2y Ban Nha), Real Madrid \u0111ang g\u1ea1 g\u1eabm Bayern Munich trao \u0111\u1ed5i Gareth Bale l\u1ea5y Robert Lewandowski trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 n\u0103m nay. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 t\u1edd b\u00e1o n\u00e0y cho bi\u1ebft Lewy \u0111\u00e3 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Bernabeu nh\u01b0ng Bale l\u1ea1i mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Premier League h\u01a1n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn Bundesliga thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\u0110\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao x\u1ee9 Wales khi\u1ebfn Real kh\u00f3 trao \u0111\u1ed5i anh l\u1ea5y \u201cs\u00e1t th\u1ee7\u201d ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ba Lan c\u1ee7a Bayern nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 MU \u0111\u00f3n Bale t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Chelsea c\u0169ng \u0111ang r\u00e1o ri\u1ebft s\u0103n Lewandowski sau khi \u0111ang m\u1ea5t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u1edbi t\u00e2n binh Alvaro Morata.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Suarez \u201cb\u00e1o tin vui\u201d v\u1ec1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 60 tri\u1ec7u euro c\u1ee7a MU</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ngu\u1ed3n tin th\u00e2n c\u1eadn t\u1eeb t\u1edd Don Balon cho bi\u1ebft, MU \u0111ang c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi ra 60 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Samuel Umtiti v\u1edbi Barcelona ngay h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Nou Camp c\u0169ng \u0111ang g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 tr\u00ec tr\u1ec7 trong vi\u1ec7c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, Luis Suarez \u2013 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Umtiti \u1edf Barca c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng anh tin c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 23 c\u1ee7a CLB n\u00e0y hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i s\u1ebd ra \u0111i trong \u201cphi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8\u201d n\u0103m nay.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>D\u00f9 v\u1eady, MU s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c khi c\u1ea3 Chelsea v\u00e0 Man City c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u0103m le mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng m\u1edbi 24 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ec3 gia c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Ibrahimovic ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay MU: Ra \u0111i nh\u01b0 \u201cv\u1ecb th\u1ea7n\u201d, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ngh\u1eb9n ng\u00e0o\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-23/mu7-1521803370-358-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Ibrahimovic ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay MU: Ra \u0111i nh\u01b0 \u201cv\u1ecb th\u1ea7n\u201d, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ngh\u1eb9n ng\u00e0o</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>N\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay MU, Ibra v\u1eabn coi m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u201cv\u1ecb th\u1ea7n\u201d.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"chuyen-nhuong-mu-ibra-doi-so-ao-chinh-thuc-gia-nhap-dai-gia-nuoc-my-c409a947329.html","id":"443"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 B\u1ea3y, ng\u00e0y 24/03/2018 00:00 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 24/3: Argentina chia r\u1ebd v\u00ec Dybala v\u00e0 Icardi","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-09/thumbnail/960-1520600242-943-width640height480.jpg","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-947308\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-947308\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Argentina chia r\u1ebd v\u00ec Dybala v\u00e0 Icardi. </strong>HLV Jorge Sampaoli m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1, \u00f4ng s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecdn 1 trong 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean, Paulo Dybala ho\u1eb7c Mauro Icardi tham d\u1ef1 VCK World Cup 2018. Ngay sau tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 n\u00e0y, x\u1ee9 s\u1edf Tango n\u1ea3y ra cu\u1ed9c tranh lu\u1eadn xem Dybala v\u00e0 Icardi, ai x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Nga m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111ang nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 Dybala, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng NHM \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Icardi c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t cao.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 24/3: Argentina chia r\u1ebd v\u00ec Dybala v\u00e0 Icardi - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-23/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-24-3-Argentina-chia-re-vi-Dybala-va-Icardi-sas-1356-1521823709-375-width660height373.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina tranh c\u00e3i quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t v\u00ec Icardi v\u00e0 Dybala</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Sao tr\u1ebb Everton \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng thay Joe Hart. </strong>HLV Gareth Southgate kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Jordan Pickford s\u1ebd b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh \u1edf tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu gi\u1eefa \u0110T Anh v\u00e0 \u0110T H\u00e0 Lan. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Everton \u0111ang g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 n\u00e0y. Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Joe Hart ph\u1ea3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf West Ham, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Pickford \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao.</p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Olivier Giroud d\u1ef1 t\u00ednh r\u1eddi Chelsea. </strong>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Olivier Giroud gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng. Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge. Ngo\u00e0i ra, theo Daily Mail, Giroud c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, trong \u0111\u00f3 Marseille v\u00e0 Lyon l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. </strong>Theo c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a L\u0110B\u0110 Anh, c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR (video assistant referee) - c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i th\u00f4ng qua video, s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a gi\u1edbi quan ch\u1ee9c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 n\u00e0y v\u00e0o t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2019/20.</p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>\u0110\u1ea1i gia Anh \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec \u201ch\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\u201d MU.</strong> Trung v\u1ec7 Jonny Evans \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, t\u1eeb Man City, Arsenal \u0111\u1ebfn Tottenham. C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 MU n\u00e0y c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n West Brom. Theo \u0111\u00f3, n\u1ebfu West Brom xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng th\u00ec Evans ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 3 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Do v\u1eady, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia \u0111ang c\u1ea1nh tranh quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1eafc Ireland.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Ibrahimovic ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay MU: Ra \u0111i nh\u01b0 \u201cv\u1ecb th\u1ea7n\u201d, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ngh\u1eb9n ng\u00e0o\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-23/mu7-1521803370-358-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Ibrahimovic ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay MU: Ra \u0111i nh\u01b0 \u201cv\u1ecb th\u1ea7n\u201d, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ngh\u1eb9n ng\u00e0o</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>N\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay MU, Ibra v\u1eabn coi m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u201cv\u1ecb th\u1ea7n\u201d.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-24-3-argentina-chia-re-vi-dybala-va-icardi-c409a947308.html","id":"442"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 S\u00e1u, ng\u00e0y 23/03/2018 00:52 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 23/3: Ronaldo t\u00edch c\u1ef1c chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Salah","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-09/thumbnail/960-1520600242-943-width640height480.jpg","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-947045\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-947045\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Ronaldo t\u00edch c\u1ef1c chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Salah.</strong> \u0110T B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Ai C\u1eadp v\u00e0o r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng 24/3 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1edf d\u0129 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fa \u00fd b\u1edfi m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c gi\u1eefa hai c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111ang ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt - si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111ang n\u1ed5i \u0111\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1m t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, Mohamed Salah. Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh ghi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh CR7 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c cho m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 v\u1edbi Salah.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 23/3: Ronaldo t\u00edch c\u1ef1c chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Salah - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-23/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-23-3-Ronaldo-tich-cuc-chuan-bi-dai-chien-Salah-4a6f2ea900000578-0-image-a-1_1521720829150-1521740965-914-width660height440.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Ronaldo t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>R\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 thay th\u1ebf Griezmann. </strong>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Koke th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn, n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Atletico Madrid b\u00e1n Antoine Griezmann trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8, th\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Wanda Metropolitano s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ee7 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, Koke kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Atletico m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t.</p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Chelsea chi 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao Argentina. </strong>BL\u0110 Chelsea kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Alvaro Morata v\u00e0 Olivier Giroud. V\u00ec v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge \u0111ang d\u1ef1 t\u00ednh t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. Theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Daily Mail, \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 Abramovich duy\u1ec7t chi g\u00f3i chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Mauro Icardi, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111ang t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Inter Milan.</p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Klopp c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m th\u1ea7y Neymar. </strong>BL\u0110 PSG v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng r\u1ef1c l\u1eeda m\u00e0 HLV Jurgen Klopp x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng cho Liverpool. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, t\u1edd Le Parisien c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u01b0a Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p, thay th\u1ebf Unai Emery.</p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Maradona b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Messi.</strong> \u201cC\u1eadu b\u00e9 v\u00e0ng\u201d Diego Maradona l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u00eanh v\u1ef1c Lionel Messi tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018. C\u1ef1u HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Argentina cho hay, Messi kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ee9ng minh b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec cho nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch nh\u1eafm v\u00e0o m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi Maradona c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean, r\u1eb1ng Messi c\u1ee9 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng v\u1edbi t\u00e2m l\u00fd tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i nh\u01b0 khi kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Barcelona.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Ch\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ed9ng Real: Ronaldo \u0111\u00f2i mua \u201cMessi Ai C\u1eadp\u201d, 150 tri\u1ec7u euro chi ngay\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-22/sa2-1521729702-792-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Ch\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ed9ng Real: Ronaldo \u0111\u00f2i mua \u201cMessi Ai C\u1eadp\u201d, 150 tri\u1ec7u euro chi ngay</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Salah, th\u00fac \u00e9p Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Liverpool.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-23-3-ronaldo-tich-cuc-chuan-bi-dai-chien-salah-c409a947045.html","id":"441"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 N\u0103m, ng\u00e0y 22/03/2018 03:00 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 22/3: L\u1ed9 l\u00ed do Real kh\u00f4ng mua Harry Kane","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-09/thumbnail/960-1520600242-943-width640height480.jpg","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-946787\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-946787\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Real kh\u00f4ng mua Kane v\u00ec lo \"bom x\u1ecbt\":</strong> Th\u00f4ng tin Real Madrid \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Robert Lewandowski khi\u1ebfn b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi \"ng\u00e3&nbsp;ng\u1eeda\" b\u1edfi tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Harry Kane m\u1edbi l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a \"\u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia\".</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 22/3: L\u1ed9 l\u00ed do Real kh\u00f4ng mua Harry Kane - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-21/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-22-3-Lo-li-do-Real-khong-mua-Harry-Kane-dsafsfs-1521647663-596-width660height371.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed \u0111\u1eaft \u0111\u1ecf, Harry Kane \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 \"hi\u1ec1n l\u00e0nh\" \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Real</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u1eeb AS, Real t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i mua Kane m\u1ed9t m\u1eb7t v\u00ec&nbsp;m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng d\u00e0nh cho ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 24 tu\u1ed5i qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft. M\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, HLV Zinedine Zidane v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino Perez lo s\u1ee3 t\u00ednh c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec1n l\u00e0nh s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Kane kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu n\u1ed5i \u00e1p l\u1ef1c kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 t\u1eeb s\u00e2n Bernabeu.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Sao Tottenham&nbsp;gi\u1ecfi h\u01a1n Modric l\u00e0m r\u00f5 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai: </strong>C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Harry Kane, Christian Eriksen l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t&nbsp;c\u1ee7a Tottenham v\u00e0 Premier League. T\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real Madrid, Barca \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft. Tuy nhi\u00ean tr\u00ean b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi qu\u00ea nh\u00e0,&nbsp;Eriksen tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 anh \"\u0111ang c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i Tottenham\"</p>\r\n\r\n<p>C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y, Age Hareide - HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110an M\u1ea1ch m\u1ea1nh mi\u1ec7ng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 c\u1eadu tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng c\u00f2n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u01a1n ng\u00f4i sao thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Real Madrid, Luka Modric.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i MU ch\u00ea Mourinho \u00edch k\u1ec9 v\u00ec v\u00f9i d\u1eadp&nbsp;Luke Shaw: </strong>Luke Shaw m\u1edbi ra s\u00e2n t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 15 tr\u1eadn k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a v\u00e0 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb HLV Jose Mourinho ch\u00ea bai. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft FA Cup g\u1eb7p Brighton (MU th\u1eafng 2-0), h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 22 tu\u1ed5i ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n ngay sau hi\u1ec7p 1.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch h\u00e0nh x\u1eed c\u1ee7a Mourinho v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Gary Neville h\u1ebft l\u1eddi ch\u00ea bai chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u0110N, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng \u0111ang ph\u00ed th\u1eddi gian cho nh\u1eefng chuy\u1ec7n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n thay v\u00ec gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 chung c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\"Luke Shaw kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00fang kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1i MU. S\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u x\u1ea5u h\u1ed5 n\u1ebfu c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u1ea3i c\u00fai \u0111\u1ea7u r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi CLB. Tr\u00ean h\u1ebft, t\u1eeb c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n gi\u1eefa Mourinho v\u1edbi Shaw, Pogba \u0111\u1ebfn Sanchez, t\u00f4i&nbsp;c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y Mourinho \u0111ang ph\u00e2n t\u00e2m b\u1edfi v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, thay v\u00ec nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn h\u01a1n trong \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y\", tr\u00edch l\u1eddi c\u1ef1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 43 tu\u1ed5i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Messi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \"n\u1eef ho\u00e0ng truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh\" \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9</strong><strong>:</strong> Oprah Winfrey l\u00e0 MC, di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean, ca- nh\u1ea1c s\u0129 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng c\u1ee7a M\u1ef9. Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \"x\u1ee9 s\u1edf c\u1edd hoa\" kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 World Cup, \"n\u1eef ho\u00e0ng truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh\"&nbsp;\u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng khai&nbsp;\u1ee7ng h\u1ed9... \u0110T Argentina v\u00e0 Lionel Messi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\"Messi, c\u1eadu&nbsp;l\u00e0 th\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a gia \u0111\u00ecnh t\u00f4i. H\u00e3y ph\u00e1t huy s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh, t\u00e0i&nbsp; n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, h\u1ee1i ch\u00e0ng chi\u1ebfn binh\", tr\u00edch l\u1eddi ng\u00f4i sao 64 tu\u1ed5i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>HLV \u0110\u1ee9c \"d\u1ed7 d\u00e0nh\" m\u1ef9 nam Marco Reus: </strong>C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Mario Gotze,&nbsp;Marco Reus kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ee3t tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c. L\u00ed gi\u1ea3i cho quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u00ean, HLV Joachim Low b\u1ed9c b\u1ea1ch: \"Reus l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a c\u00fang t\u00f4i.&nbsp;Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf CLB&nbsp;\u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n\".&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"N\u00f3ng: Real \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Lewandowski 100 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p Ronaldo\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-21/1521626116-730-thumbnail.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">N\u00f3ng: Real \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Lewandowski 100 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p Ronaldo</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>Lewandowski (Bayern Munich) v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn \u0111\u1ebfn Real Madrid ngay h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-22-3-lo-li-do-real-khong-mua-harry-kane-c409a946787.html","id":"440"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 T\u01b0, ng\u00e0y 21/03/2018 05:37 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 21/3: Messi l\u1ed9 l\u00ed do h\u00f3a \"si\u00eau nh\u00e2n\" tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-09/thumbnail/960-1520600242-943-width640height480.jpg","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-946530\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-946530\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Messi h\u00e9 l\u1ed9 l\u00ed do h\u1ebft n\u00f4n khan, h\u00f3a \"si\u00eau nh\u00e2n\" tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i:</strong> C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian, NHM t\u1eebng lo s\u1ed1t v\u00f3 khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Lionel Messi c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed n\u00f4n khan tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Barca l\u1eabn \u0110T Argentina. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ti\u1ebfp di\u1ec5n kho\u1ea3ng 1 n\u0103m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 21/3: Messi l\u1ed9 l\u00ed do h\u00f3a &amp;#34;si\u00eau nh\u00e2n&amp;#34; tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-21/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-21-3-Messi-lo-li-do-hoa-dfsg-1521579926-664-width660height440.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Messi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thay \u0111\u1ed5i th\u00f3i quen dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng v\u00ec s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u1eeb si\u00eau sao 30 tu\u1ed5i, b\u00ed quy\u1ebft gi\u00fap anh kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 do thay \u0111\u1ed5i ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9, th\u00f3i quen \u0103n u\u1ed1ng b\u1eefa b\u00e3i: \u201cTh\u1eddi gian \u1ea5y, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7 khi t\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 v\u00e0o mi\u1ec7ng: s\u00f4 c\u00f4 la, b\u00e1nh quy, pizza, \u0111\u1ed3 u\u1ed1ng c\u00f3 ga, khi\u1ebfn s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe gi\u1ea3m s\u00fat v\u00e0 nh\u01b0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed3 b\u1ecf \u0111i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, t\u00f4i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3\u201d.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Sao MU t\u1eebng gh\u00e9t cay gh\u00e9t \u0111\u1eafng Sanchez:</strong> Tr\u00ean k\u00eanh TyC Sports (Argentina), h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Marcos Rojo khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u201cng\u00e3 ng\u1eeda: khi ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1edbi Alexis Sanchez trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\u201cAlexis l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi nh\u01b0ng th\u00fa th\u1ef1c, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u01b0a nhau m\u1ea5y tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf. M\u1ed7i khi MU \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Arsenal hay Argentina g\u1eb7p Chile, t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n cho anh ta \u0103n m\u1ed9t c\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, t\u00f4i t\u1eebng kh\u00f4ng tin v\u00e0o m\u1eaft m\u00ecnh khi bi\u1ebft MU c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Sanchez, gi\u1edd th\u00ec anh ta \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i r\u1ed3i\u201d, tr\u00edch l\u1eddi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 28 tu\u1ed5i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Real v\u1ee1 m\u1ed9ng mua \u201cMessi trong khung g\u1ed7\u201d: </strong>Alisson l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a AS Roma c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0110T Brazil, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00ed nh\u01b0 \u201cMessi trong khung g\u1ed7\u201d. T\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm hai \u201c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn\u201d Real Madrid v\u00e0 Liverpool.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tuy nhi\u00ean m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Alisson kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 m\u00ecnh \u0111ang t\u1eadp trung to\u00e0n l\u1ef1c cho CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n Roma, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi ch\u01b0a ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c ra \u0111i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>V\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c MU tr\u1ecdng th\u01b0\u1edfng, Young \u0111\u00e3 \u201cd\u1ea1y d\u1ed7\u201d \u0111\u00e0n em:</strong> Ashley Young v\u1eeba nh\u1eadn tin vui khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c MU gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u00eam 1 n\u0103m. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a, ng\u00f4i sao 32 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea9y t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Luke Shaw v\u00e0o \u201cng\u00f5 c\u1ee5t\u201d. C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a l\u00e2u, HLV Jose Mourinho th\u1eb3ng th\u1eebng ch\u00ea bai h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 22 tu\u1ed5i sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Brighton 2-0 \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft FA Cup.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, Young \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u00e0n em: \u201cKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 Shaw m\u00e0 c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t cho c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n gi\u1eef c\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ec9nh t\u00e1o v\u00e0 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n th\u1eadt ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9. T\u00f4i tin Shaw s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai\u201d.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Sao Liverpool kh\u00f4ng h\u1ed1i h\u1eadn v\u00ec t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec7 t\u1eed Pep:</strong> Tr\u00ean Daily Mail, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Emre Can x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Pep Guardiola li\u00ean h\u1ec7 th\u1eddi c\u00f2n d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Bayern Munich \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2015/16 nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eb3ng th\u1eebng kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh kh\u00f4ng h\u1ed1i h\u1eadn v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y v\u00ec \u0111ang l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia t\u00e0i n\u0103ng kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m, Jurgen Klopp.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Barcelona: \u201dTam gi\u00e1c qu\u1ef7\u201d d\u1ea7n s\u1ea1ch b\u00f3ng, ai gi\u00fap Messi - Coutinho?\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-16/barce_midfield-640-1521174625-600-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Barcelona: \u201dTam gi\u00e1c qu\u1ef7\u201d d\u1ea7n s\u1ea1ch b\u00f3ng, ai gi\u00fap Messi - Coutinho?</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>Barcelona \u0111ang d\u1ea7n chia tay v\u1edbi th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao sau 1 th\u1eadp k\u1ef7.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-21-3-messi-lo-li-do-hoa-sieu-nhan-tro-lai-c409a946530.html","id":"439"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 T\u01b0, ng\u00e0y 21/03/2018 03:51 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: N\u1ed5 \u201cbom t\u1ea5n k\u00e9p\u201d Arsenal sau Sanchez","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-09/thumbnail/960-1520600242-943-width640height480.jpg","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-946529\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-946529\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>MU g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c: N\u1ed5 \u201cbom t\u1ea5n k\u00e9p\" Arsenal</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua, gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n MU \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecfi mua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Hector Bellerin c\u1ee7a Arsenal nh\u01b0 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p thay th\u1ebf Antonio Valencia trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. Tuy nhi\u00ean ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf \u201cPh\u00e1o th\u1ee7\u201d l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: N\u1ed5 \u201cbom t\u1ea5n k\u00e9p\u201d Arsenal sau Sanchez - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-21/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-No-bom-tan-kep-Arsenal-sau-Sanchez----twtewe-1521577203-190-width660height495.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 Bellerin, MU c\u00f2n t\u00ednh \"cu\u1ed7m\" lu\u00f4n Ramsey t\u1eeb Arsenal</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u1eeb Telegraph, HLV Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t v\u1edbi BL\u0110 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea3 Aaron Ramsey (m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed ch\u01b0a ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9). M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 27 tu\u1ed5i g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c&nbsp;c\u1ea1nh tranh&nbsp;su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh (m\u1edbi ra s\u00e2n 23 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng, ghi 7 b\u00e0n).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Tottenham quy\u1ebft tranh Bale</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 t\u1edd b\u00e1o \u1edf TBN v\u00e0 Anh \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0a tin Gareth Bale b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u201cl\u1eadt k\u00e8o\u201d MU sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 Champions League v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i nh\u00e0m ch\u00e1n. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Tottenham.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\u0110\u1ebfn h\u00f4m nay, Daily Star x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn ph\u00eda \u201cG\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng\u201d c\u0169ng quy\u1ebft c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi MU \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n Bale tr\u1edf v\u1ec1. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf ch\u1ed7, HLV Mauricio Pochettino v\u00e0 gi\u1edbi l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn&nbsp;m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed 100 tri\u1ec7u euro (89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng) m\u00e0 Real \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Tottenham \u201cch\u1ed1t\u201d gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Lukaku</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Toby Alderweireld l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u201chot\u201d nh\u1ea5t th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh MU, ng\u00f4i sao thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Tottenham c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 Real Madrid, PSG, Chelsea quan t\u00e2m nh\u1edd \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1t c\u1ea3 trung v\u1ec7 l\u1eabn h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng gi\u1eefa c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 \u201cG\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng\u201d c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n t\u1edbi h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2019, m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng kho\u1ea3ng 29 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean theo Daily Star, BL\u0110 Tottenham s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ng\u1ed3i v\u00e0o b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n ngay t\u1eeb b\u00e2y gi\u1edd n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c n\u00e0o tr\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ee7 42 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Chelsea chi\u1ebfm \u01b0u th\u1ebf v\u1ee5 Luke Shaw</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>MU nh\u1eafm Alderweireld, \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Luke Shaw \u1edf s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ed3i k\u1ebft. Tuy nhi\u00ean h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 22 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n qu\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng b\u1edfi h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Anh nh\u01b0 Chelsea, Arsenal, Liverpool, Everton \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng dang tay c\u1ee9u v\u1edbt anh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb Mirror cho hay, Chelsea \u0111ang chi\u1ebfm \u01b0u th\u1ebf h\u01a1n c\u1ea3, m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n v\u00ec \u0111\u00e1p&nbsp;\u1ee9ng m\u1ecdi y\u00eau c\u1ea7u v\u1ec1 ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1eabn l\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ed5ng (Shaw \u0111ang nh\u1eadn 80 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/ tu\u1ea7n \u1edf MU), m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n v\u00ec b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u201cThe Blues\u201d.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Sao Napoli l\u1ea1i \"b\u1eadt \u0111\u00e8n xanh\"</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Jorginho, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Napoli \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean tr\u00ean k\u00eanh ph\u00e1t thanh Radio Crc (Italia), Joao Santos \u2013 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 qu\u1ed1c gia Italia x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u1eddi m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi n\u00e0o t\u1eeb ph\u00eda MU.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Lukaku k\u1ebft th\u00e2n Sanchez, phe Mourinho c\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh: Pogba s\u1eafp ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-21/640lu1-1521566767-992-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Lukaku k\u1ebft th\u00e2n Sanchez, phe Mourinho c\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh: Pogba s\u1eafp ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>Nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y Paul Pogba \u0111ang b\u1ecb c\u00f4 l\u1eadp tai Old Trafford.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"chuyen-nhuong-mu-no-bom-tan-kep-arsenal-sau-sanchez-c409a946529.html","id":"438"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 Ba, ng\u00e0y 20/03/2018 05:22 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 20/3: HLV tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Pogba","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-09/thumbnail/960-1520600242-943-width640height480.jpg","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-946304\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-946304\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>HLV tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Pogba:</strong> \u0110T Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u00e0n l\u00e0m n\u00f3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi 2 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu g\u1eb7p Colombia v\u00e0 Nga. HLV Deschamps x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh Pogba l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 then ch\u1ed1t n\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o: \u201cPogba \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf MU. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf l\u1ea1i m\u1ecdi r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i t\u1ea1i Anh v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung t\u1ed1i \u0111a cho \u0110TQG v\u00e0 World Cup 2018\u201d.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 20/3: HLV tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Pogba - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-20/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-20-3-HLV-tuyen-Phap-canh-bao-Pogba-hot-pog-1521497088-535-width660height440.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p c\u1ea7n Pogba \u0111\u1ec3 \u00f4m m\u1ed9ng l\u1edbn World Cup 2018</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Shaw s\u1ebd hay nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u1ebfu r\u1eddi MU:</strong> Paul Scholes \u0111ang \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Luke Shaw r\u1eddi MU trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Theo \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u201cQu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\u201d, Shaw s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n t\u1ed1i \u0111a \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n, \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 HLV Mourinho \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ronaldinho l\u1ea5y l\u00f2ng c\u1ea3 Messi v\u00e0 Ronaldo: </strong>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m sinh nh\u1eadt tu\u1ed5i 38, Ronaldinho \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 hai si\u00eau sao b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea1i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t. Theo \u0111\u00f3, \u201cRo v\u1ea9u\u201d nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng h\u1ed3i k\u1ebft gi\u1eefa Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi mang l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ee3i \u00edch cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. NHM \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh hi\u1ebfm c\u00f3 gi\u1eefa hai thi\u00ean t\u00e0i xu\u1ea5t ch\u00fang nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Hazard \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i t\u1ef1 do \u1edf \u0110T B\u1ec9: </strong>HLV Martinez kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a HLV Conte t\u1ea1i Chelsea. Th\u1eddi gian qua, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1eaft Hazard \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t \u201cs\u1ed1 9\u201d th\u1ef1c th\u1ee5. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn Hazard kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t huy&nbsp; t\u1ed1i \u0111a s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111i b\u00f3ng, ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ph\u00e1 r\u1ed1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Kane 175 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u1eaft h\u01a1n Messi:</strong> Theo \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Cies Football Observatory, gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Kane hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 175 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n Messi 2 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n b\u1edfi Kane \u00edt h\u01a1n Leo 6 tu\u1ed5i. Tottenham c\u0169ng s\u1ebd ki\u1ebfm b\u1ed9n ti\u1ec1n n\u1ebfu b\u00e1n Dele Alli, b\u1edfi c\u0169ng theo ngu\u1ed3n \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 tr\u00ean, sao tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 139 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u1eaft th\u1ee9 3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: B\u1ea1o chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng quy\u1ebft mua sao Arsenal\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-20/1521483490-968-thumbnail.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: B\u1ea1o chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng quy\u1ebft mua sao Arsenal</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>MU \u0111ang c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Arsenal ngay h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-20-3-hlv-tuyen-phap-canh-bao-pogba-c409a946304.html","id":"437"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 Ba, ng\u00e0y 20/03/2018 03:17 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: B\u1ea1o chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng quy\u1ebft mua sao Arsenal","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-09/thumbnail/960-1520600242-943-width640height480.jpg","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-946298\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-946298\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, MU quy\u1ebft th\u1eafng Juventus \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 sao Arsenal</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Daily Mirror cho bi\u1ebft, hi\u1ec7n <strong>MU </strong>\u0111ang s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0 Arsenal y\u00eau c\u1ea7u trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn Hector Bellerin v\u00e0o h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Hi\u1ec7n Juventus c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u0103m le mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u1ee7a \u201cPh\u00e1o th\u1ee7\u201d.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: B\u1ea1o chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng quy\u1ebft mua sao Arsenal - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-20/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-Bao-chi-50-trieu-bang-quyet-mua-sao-Arsenal-noticia-hector-belerin-1521483544-42-width660height371.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Bellerin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3 MU v\u00e0 Juve quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t</p>\r\n\r\n<p>H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Bellerin v\u1edbi Arsenal c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eadn n\u0103m 2023. Nh\u01b0ng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o \u1edf l\u00f2 La Masia c\u1ee7a Barca \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a HLV Arsene Wenger v\u00e0 anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd s\u1edbm ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 mua 4-5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ra gi\u00e1 \u201cc\u1ef1c kh\u1ee7ng\u201d mua tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Chelsea</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>MU</em> \u0111ang t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi Luke Shaw kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00f2n Ashley Young \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00e1 cao tu\u1ed5i. C\u00e1i t\u00ean m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0 Marcos Alonso v\u00e0 theo t\u1edd Don Balon (T\u00e2y Ban Nha), Man \u0111\u1ecf s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi \u0111\u1ebfn 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d n\u00e0y th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ngay h\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao khi Alonso v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1eaft x\u00edch kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00ean c\u00f4ng v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a \u201cThe Blues\u201d su\u1ed1t 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Mourinho ru\u1ed3ng r\u1eaby Luke Shaw, Tottenham v\u00e0 Chelsea tranh nhau xin \u201cgi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u\u201d</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>T\u1edd Daily Star cho hay, HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u1edbi Luke Shaw v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng thanh l\u00fd h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i m\u00e0 <u>MU</u> t\u1eebng ph\u1ea3i chi \u0111\u1ebfn 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua anh v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Southampton h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2014.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang c\u00f3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i th\u00e0nh London l\u00e0 Chelsea v\u00e0 Tottenham s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng dang tay ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i n\u1ebfu anh r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Old Trafford khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y k\u1ebft th\u00fac.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Young \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u01b0\u1edfng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ngu\u1ed3n tin uy t\u00edn t\u1eeb MEN Sport cho bi\u1ebft, nh\u1eb1m t\u1eb7ng th\u01b0\u1edfng cho nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a Ashley Young m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, BL\u0110 MU \u0111\u00e3 v\u1eeba cung c\u1ea5p cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean v\u1eeba k\u00fd k\u1ebft th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Theo \u0111\u00f3, anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi \u201cNh\u00e0 h\u00e1t c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1\u201d th\u00eam 1 n\u0103m, ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y m\u1edbi h\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi \u201cQu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\u201d.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>\u201cPh\u00e1 k\u00e9t\u201d mua \u201csao mai\u201d 17 tu\u1ed5i</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Sun kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, MU \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed trinh s\u00e1t theo d\u00f5i g\u1eaft gao Ryan Sessegnon v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00ean b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y nh\u1eb1m thay th\u1ebf Luke Shaw s\u1eafp ra \u0111i. Hi\u1ec7n ngo\u00e0i \u201cQu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\u201d, Liverpool v\u00e0 Tottenham c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u0103m le mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tu\u1ed5i teen \u0111ang r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Craven Cottage.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><div style=\"text-align: center;width: 100%;clear: both;position: relative;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"position:relative;max-width: 660px;margin: 0 auto\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: B\u1ea1o chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng quy\u1ebft mua sao Arsenal - 2\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-20/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-Bao-chi-50-trieu-bang-quyet-mua-sao-Arsenal-9282042301-1521483544-594-width660height439.jpg\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"24h-banner-in-image\" style=\"position: absolute;display: block;overflow: hidden;width: 660px;height: 90px;color: white;bottom: 0px;left: 0px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"24h-banner-in-image-close\" style=\"top:5px;right: 5px;position: absolute;display: none;overflow: hidden;width: 22px;height: 22px;color: #ccc;font-size: large;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: B\u1ea1o chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng quy\u1ebft mua sao Arsenal - 3\" onclick=\"in_image_close();\" id=\"in-image-close\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/24h_banner_image_library/in-image-close.svg\"></img>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n                \r\n            </div></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Ryan Sessegnon (Fulham) l\u00e0 \"sao mai\" \u0111ang l\u00ean c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"MU \u0111en \u0111\u1ee7i \u0111\u1ee5ng Tottenham FA Cup: Mourinho b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u00fd tr\u1eddi?\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-19/1521427412-670-thumbnail.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">MU \u0111en \u0111\u1ee7i \u0111\u1ee5ng Tottenham FA Cup: Mourinho b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u00fd tr\u1eddi?</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>L\u00e0n s\u00f3ng \u0111\u00f2i sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho d\u00e2ng cao trong C\u0110V MU, \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u1ebd t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"chuyen-nhuong-mu-bao-chi-50-trieu-bang-quyet-mua-sao-arsenal-c409a946298.html","id":"436"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 Hai, ng\u00e0y 19/03/2018 00:15 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 19/3: Ti\u00ean tri d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o Neymar l\u1ee1 World Cup","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-09/thumbnail/960-1520600242-943-width640height480.jpg","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-946001\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-946001\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Ti\u00ean tri d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o Neymar l\u1ee1 World Cup:</strong> H\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 12 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, trong m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh \u1edf Nam M\u1ef9, nh\u00e0 ti\u00ean tri Carlinhos Vidente \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Neymar s\u1ebd ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eeb 5-7 th\u00e1ng v\u00ec ca ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018. \u00d4ng c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi (ch\u1ec9 v\u1ec1 th\u1ee9 3) d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 19/3: Ti\u00ean tri d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o Neymar l\u1ee1 World Cup - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-18/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-19-3-Tien-tri-du-bao-Neymar-lo-World-Cup-neymar-1521380571-92-width660height445.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Neymar trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u00e0n ch\u00e2n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, Neymar \u0111\u00e3 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00e1 n\u1eb7ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn PSG th\u1eafng Marseille h\u1ed3i cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t ca ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt. C\u00e1c b\u00e1c s\u1ef9 n\u00f3i \u201cTi\u1ec3u Pele\u201d s\u1ebd r\u1eddi xa s\u00e2n c\u1ecf trong v\u00f2ng 2-3 th\u00e1ng, ch\u1ec9 b\u1eb1ng n\u1eeda th\u1eddi gian m\u00e0 ti\u00ean tri Carlinhos n\u00f3i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Real Madrid t\u00ecm \u201cti\u1ec3u Modric\u201d: </strong>T\u1edd Marca \u0111\u01b0a tin, Real Madrid b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi k\u1ebf nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Luka Modric. Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino Perez \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 32 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh m\u1eabu cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c, do v\u1eady, \u201cLos Blancos\u201d s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng trong vi\u1ec7c s\u0103n ng\u01b0\u1eddi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Salah tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng s\u1ee3 Man City: </strong>Sau l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m di\u1ec5n ra h\u00f4m th\u1ee9 S\u00e1u, l\u00e1 th\u0103m may r\u1ee7i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a Liverpool ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Man City \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League. Man xanh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng Salah kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, \u201cThe Kop\u201d kh\u00f4ng ng\u00e1n d\u00f9 b\u1ea5t k\u00ec \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 ai v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng cao nh\u1ea5t.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Bayern t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed5i James l\u1ea5y Dembele:</strong> Theo Don Balon, Bayern Munich \u0111ang t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi James Rodriguez r\u1ed3i sau n\u00e0y d\u00f9ng anh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ea5y ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ousmane Dembele c\u1ee7a Barca trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng quay v\u1ec1 Real Madrid n\u1ebfu Zinedine Zidane r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi CLB.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Barca ch\u1ea5m Isco thay Iniesta: </strong>Andres Iniesta, 34 tu\u1ed5i, v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1 cho Barca hay ra \u0111i. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, hay \u0111\u1ea1i gia Trung Qu\u1ed1c ng\u1ecf \u00fd mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ini. Barca mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u01b0ng song song v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng. Isco c\u1ee7a Real l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u201cBlaugrana\u201d th\u00e8m mu\u1ed1n, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 kho\u1ea3ng 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Terry v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u:</strong> Trung v\u1ec7 k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u John Terry,&nbsp;37 tu\u1ed5i, kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, anh v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00eam 1 n\u0103m n\u1eefa cho Aston Villa. Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n l\u1eabn tinh th\u1ea7n cho tham v\u1ecdng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Neymar ch\u00e1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p, Real s\u0103n \u0111\u00f3n: \u201cB\u1ed1 gi\u00e0\u201d khi\u1ebfn PSG ph\u00e1t \u0111i\u00ean\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-17/psg1-1521299008-171-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Neymar ch\u00e1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p, Real s\u0103n \u0111\u00f3n: \u201cB\u1ed1 gi\u00e0\u201d khi\u1ebfn PSG ph\u00e1t \u0111i\u00ean</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>Theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Neymar \u0111ang c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y qu\u00e1 ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u Ligue I.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-19-3-tien-tri-du-bao-neymar-lo-world-cup-c409a946001.html","id":"435"},{"date":"Ch\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt, ng\u00e0y 18/03/2018 05:04 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 18/3: Zidane t\u1ef1 tin k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p Ronaldo - Neymar","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-09/thumbnail/960-1520600242-943-width640height480.jpg","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-945872\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-945872\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Zidane t\u1ef1 tin k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p Neymar v\u00e0 Ronaldo: </strong>Trong m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, HLV Zinedine Zidane \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i Neymar. M\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p&nbsp;c\u0169ng t\u1ef1 tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \"ti\u1ec3u Pele\" s\u1ebd h\u00f2a h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u00e1c si\u00eau sao tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Real nh\u01b0 Ronaldo, Bale, Benzema n\u1ebfu BL\u0110 \"\u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia\" mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 anh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 18/3: Zidane t\u1ef1 tin k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p Ronaldo - Neymar - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-18/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-18-3-Zidane-tu-tin-ket-hop-Ronaldo---Neymar-dsafsdfsd-1521314131-42-width660height411.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Zidane t\u1ef1 tin Neymar c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \"h\u00f2a h\u1ee3p\" v\u1edbi Ronaldo v\u00e0 c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Real</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\"Neymar l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng&nbsp;kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i cho Real. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y&nbsp;s\u1ebd gi\u00fap cho h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n hay kh\u00f4ng \u00e0? T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft. M\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3&nbsp;kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u00e0i n\u0103ng \u1edf m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, ch\u01a1i \u1edf b\u1ea5t k\u00ec v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0o v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i, phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a CLB&nbsp;c\u0169ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady\".</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>\"Mourinho \u0111ang k\u00ecm h\u00e3m Pogba, Sanchez\": </strong>\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1eddi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Alan Shearer sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn HLV Jose Mourinho l\u00fang t\u00fang trong vi\u1ec7c k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa&nbsp;Paul Pogba v\u00e0 Alexis Sanchez su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian qua.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\"MU chi 90 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Pogba nh\u01b0ng Mourinho v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch khai th\u00e1c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Pogba th\u1eadm ch\u00ed&nbsp;kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 hay t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Sanchez c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1 h\u01a1n, c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m t\u01b0\u1edfng MU ch\u1ec9 mua v\u1ec1 c\u00e1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u sa s\u00fat d\u01b0\u1edbi tay Mourinho\", tr\u00edch l\u1eddi c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 47 tu\u1ed5i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>\"Real, Barca l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u1ed1 1 v\u00ec s\u1edf h\u1eefu Ronaldo, Messi\":</strong> \u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng CLB l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League, HLV Carlo Ancelotti kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea7n ng\u1ea1i \"\u0111\u1eb7t c\u1eeda\" cho Real Madrid v\u00e0 Barca. Theo chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia,&nbsp;hai g\u00e3 kh\u1ed3ng l\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m n\u00ean kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t: Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 Lionel Messi.</p><p></p>\r\n\r\n<p>M\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, Ancelotti c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao hai CLB qu\u00ea nh\u00e0, Juventus v\u00e0 AS Roma - nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Real, Barca \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft: \"Real v\u00e0 Barca \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t v\u00ec kinh nghi\u1ec7m, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1edf Champions League c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 s\u1edf h\u1eefu Ronaldo, Messi.&nbsp;Juventus v\u00e0 Roma kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00ec ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd\".</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Courtois nguy\u1ec7n g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Chelsea: </strong>Tr\u00ean Daily Mail, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Thibaut Courtois x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn ch\u01b0a&nbsp;gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea (h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u0169 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n t\u1edbi h\u00e8 2019). Tuy nhi\u00ean, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u1eabn s\u1ebd t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n v\u00e0 \u1edf l\u1ea1i&nbsp;s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge \u00edt nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m sau.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\"H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng gi\u1eefa t\u00f4i v\u00e0 Chelsea v\u1eabn c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m sau, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u1ebfp theo\", tr\u00edch l\u1eddi Courtois.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Arsenal nh\u1eafm \"bom x\u1ecbt\" AC Milan:</strong> \u0110\u00e3 chi nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Lacazette, Aubameyang, tuy nhi\u00ean BL\u0110 Arsenal v\u1eabn l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0o k\u00ec chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018. Theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u1eeb Mirror, c\u00e1i t\u00ean l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm \"Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7\" l\u00e0 Andre Silva.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi AC Milan v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed 38 tri\u1ec7u euro, tuy nhi\u00ean ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u0110N \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1 khi ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n sau 17 tr\u1eadn ra s\u00e2n.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Neymar ch\u00e1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p, Real s\u0103n \u0111\u00f3n: \u201cB\u1ed1 gi\u00e0\u201d khi\u1ebfn PSG ph\u00e1t \u0111i\u00ean\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-17/psg1-1521299008-171-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Neymar ch\u00e1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p, Real s\u0103n \u0111\u00f3n: \u201cB\u1ed1 gi\u00e0\u201d khi\u1ebfn PSG ph\u00e1t \u0111i\u00ean</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>Theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Neymar \u0111ang c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y qu\u00e1 ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u Ligue I.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-18-3-zidane-tu-tin-ket-hop-ronaldo-neymar-c409a945872.html","id":"434"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 B\u1ea3y, ng\u00e0y 17/03/2018 05:35 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: Nh\u1edd tay si\u00eau c\u00f2, g\u1ea1 \u0111\u1ed5i Pogba l\u1ea5y sao PSG","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-09/thumbnail/960-1520600242-943-width640height480.jpg","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-945702\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-945702\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Mu\u1ed1n si\u00eau c\u00f2 gi\u00fap s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed5i Pogba l\u1ea5y sao PSG</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Theo tin t\u1eeb t\u1edd The Independent, <strong>MU</strong> \u0111ang ng\u1ea5p ngh\u00e9 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111em Paul Pogba \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Marco Verratti (PSG).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>C\u1ea3 hai ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n chung l\u00e0 Mino Raiola v\u00e0 \u201cQu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\u201d mu\u1ed1n th\u00f4ng qua \u201csi\u00eau c\u00f2\u201d danh ti\u1ebfng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd v\u1edbi m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 l\u00e0m \u0103n nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p gi\u1eefa \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u0111\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1m n\u00e0y tr\u00f3t l\u1ecdt trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: Nh\u1edd tay si\u00eau c\u00f2, g\u1ea1 \u0111\u1ed5i Pogba l\u1ea5y sao PSG - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-17/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-Nho-tay-sieu-co-ga-doi-Pogba-lay-sao-PSG-verratti_01_utfz-1521230219-147-width660height446.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Pogba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 sang PSG \u0111\u1ec3 Verratti v\u1ec1 MU</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Bale n\u00e9 MU, mu\u1ed1n sang Chelsea v\u00ec gh\u00e9t Mourinho</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Theo t\u1edd Don Balon, Gareth Bale \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1eddi Real Madrid khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay k\u1ebft th\u00fac. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n gia nh\u1eadp <em>MU</em> d\u00f9 \u201cQu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\u201d s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua anh v\u00ec cho r\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u1ec1 ra s\u1ebd c\u1ea3n tr\u1edf l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, Bale \u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc sang Chelsea ho\u1eb7c v\u1ec1 l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Tottenham Hotspur.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C&nbsp;\"tr\u00f3i ch\u00e2n\" Rojo, khi\u1ebfn PSG th\u00f4i mong ch\u1edd</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Trang ch\u1ee7 <u>MU</u> v\u1eeba x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 v\u1eeba gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Marcos Rojo \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1ng 6 n\u0103m 2021 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00eam 1 n\u0103m n\u1eefa g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi nhau. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c PSG \u2013 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 27 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina c\u1ee7a \u201cQu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\u201d s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u1eeb b\u1ecf th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: Nh\u1edd tay si\u00eau c\u00f2, g\u1ea1 \u0111\u1ed5i Pogba l\u1ea5y sao PSG - 2\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-17/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-Nho-tay-sieu-co-ga-doi-Pogba-lay-sao-PSG-7a0a1612548d4e00b7f7994ab67a0fc0-1521230219-217-width660height371.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Rojo h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi c\u00f9ng MU</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Juve l\u01b0\u1ee1ng l\u1ef1 \u201cgi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u\u201d Darmian</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>K\u00eanh truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd Calciomercato cho hay d\u00f9 Matteo Darmian r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n sang Juventus n\u1ebfu r\u1eddi MU h\u00e8 n\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n c\u00f3 v\u1ebb kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\u201cB\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0 th\u00e0nh Turin\u201d v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u0103n t\u0103n v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n l\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1ebfu chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Darmian, v\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Kwadwo Asamoah v\u00e0 Stephan Lichsteiner.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Darmian t\u1eebng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho Torino \u2013 \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a Juve \u1edf th\u00e0nh Turin v\u00e0 anh v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng n\u1ebfu h\u1ed3i h\u01b0\u01a1ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Serie A.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Kh\u00f4ng thi\u1ebfu ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u00e0i thay Pogba</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Trang footballwhispers m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y cho r\u1eb1ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Paul Pogba \u1edf MU h\u00e8 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu \u201cQu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\u201d chia tay ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 box to box ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng thay th\u1ebf anh m\u00e0 gi\u00e1 l\u1ea1i \u201cm\u1ec1m\u201d h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ee3i \u00fd l\u00e0: Allan (Napoli), Kerem Demirbay (Hoffenheim), Fred (Shakhtar Donetsk), Mario Lemina (Southampton), Max Mayer (Schalke04) v\u00e0 Wilfred Ndidi (Leicester City).</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"H\u1ecdp b\u00e1o MU - Brighton: Mourinho \u201d\u0111\u00e1 xo\u00e1y\u201d fan, v\u00ed Brighton nh\u01b0 Sevilla\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-16/sdfasdfsd-1521209769-481-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">H\u1ecdp b\u00e1o MU - Brighton: Mourinho \u201d\u0111\u00e1 xo\u00e1y\u201d fan, v\u00ed Brighton nh\u01b0 Sevilla</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>Mourinho ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 quan \u0111i\u1ec3m \"MU b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u1edf c\u00fap C1 l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng\".</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"chuyen-nhuong-mu-nho-tay-sieu-co-ga-doi-pogba-lay-sao-psg-c409a945702.html","id":"433"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 S\u00e1u, ng\u00e0y 16/03/2018 03:40 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 16/3: Chelsea thua th\u1ea3m, Hazard & Courtois kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn Real","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-09/thumbnail/960-1520600242-943-width640height480.jpg","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-945429\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-945429\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Chelsea thua th\u1ea3m, Hazard &amp; Courtois kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn Real.</strong> Theo t\u1edd Daily Mail, m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Eden Hazard v\u00e0 Thibaut Courtois tr\u01b0\u1edbc Barcelona v\u1eeba qua \u0111\u00e3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y. Theo \u0111\u00f3, BL\u0110 Real nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh hai ng\u00f4i sao tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao nh\u1ea5t. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu s\u1ebd ho\u00e3n qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Hazard v\u00e0 Courtois \u0111\u1ebfn sau World Cup 2018.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 16/3: Chelsea thua th\u1ea3m, Hazard &amp; Courtois kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn Real - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-16/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-16-3-Chelsea-thua-tham-Hazard-326751-1521135885-640-width660height515.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Real kh\u00f4ng v\u1ed9i v\u00e3 mua Hazard v\u00e0 Courtois</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Wilshere v\u1eabn c\u00f3 ch\u1ed7 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tuy\u1ec3n Anh.</strong> Theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a HLV Gareth Southgate, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jack Wilshere v\u1eabn n\u1eb1m trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay, Wilshere kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean. C\u0169ng v\u00ec v\u1eady, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Arsenal, d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Wenger thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u1edf l\u1ea1i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Lewandowski khao kh\u00e1t Champions League.</strong> Robert Lewandowski \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Bayern sau khi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Allianz Arena ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t c\u00fa \u0103n ba ch\u00f3i l\u1ecdi. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn nay, Bayern kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o \u0111\u0103ng quang c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u n\u1eefa. B\u1edfi th\u1ebf, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ba Lan c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y s\u1ed1t ru\u1ed9t v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n&nbsp; c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d chinh ph\u1ee5c Champions League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Mang s\u00fang v\u00e0o s\u00e2n, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch PAOK g\u1eb7p h\u1ecda. </strong>Theo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Hy L\u1ea1p, doanh nh\u00e2n Ivan Savvidis - Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch CLB PAOK Salonika m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi h\u00e0nh vi mang s\u00fang v\u00e0o s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh \u201cgi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft\u201d tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u1edf tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a v\u1edbi AEK Athens. Sau cu\u1ed9c \u0111i\u1ec1u tra m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, L\u0110B\u0110 Hy L\u1ea1p ra m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh x\u1eed ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Ivan Savvidis c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng PAOK Salonika.</p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Dortmund g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 khi t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay Aubameyang. </strong>Trong phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 \u0111\u00f4ng 2018 v\u1eeba qua, Dortmund b\u00e1n ch\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng Aubameyang cho Arsenal v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 56 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Sau \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c h\u1ecfi m\u01b0\u1ee3n Michy Batshuayi c\u1ee7a Chelsea. Hi\u1ec7n Dortmund \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n mua \u0111\u1ee9t Batshuayi nh\u01b0ng b\u1ecb Chelsea h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Neymar mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi PSG: MU \u0111ua bom ti\u1ec1n v\u1edbi Real, \u201cth\u1ebf l\u1ef1c ng\u1ea7m\u201d nh\u00fang tay\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-13/640x480-1520951479-442-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Neymar mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi PSG: MU \u0111ua bom ti\u1ec1n v\u1edbi Real, \u201cth\u1ebf l\u1ef1c ng\u1ea7m\u201d nh\u00fang tay</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>Real Madrid v\u00e0 MU \u0111ang l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Neymar t\u1eeb PSG.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-16-3-chelsea-thua-tham-hazard-courtois-kho-den-real-c409a945429.html","id":"432"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 N\u0103m, ng\u00e0y 15/03/2018 00:01 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: Mourinho ch\u00e1n Pogba, m\u01a1 Modric ho\u1eb7c Rakitic thay th\u1ebf","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-09/thumbnail/960-1520600242-943-width640height480.jpg","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-945136\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-945136\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Thay Pogba, Mourinho m\u01a1 t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p \u201ctr\u00f2 c\u0169\u201d Modric ho\u1eb7c mua Rakitic</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Paul Pogba, ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 BL\u0110 MU \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed1n bao c\u00f4ng s\u1ee9c v\u00e0 chi t\u1edbi 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb Juventus 18 th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a x\u1ee9ng t\u1ea7m, HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111ang mong mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 \u1edf Real Madrid l\u00e0 Luka Modric.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: Mourinho ch\u00e1n Pogba, m\u01a1 Modric ho\u1eb7c Rakitic thay th\u1ebf - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-15/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-Mourinho-chan-Pogba-mo-Modric-hoac-Rakitic-thay-the-rakitic-990x556-1521110318-137-width660height371.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Modric (s\u1ed1 10) v\u00e0 Rakitic l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1edbi nhau&nbsp;\u1edf \u0110T Croatia</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Theo Diario Gol, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia c\u1ee7a Real hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 kho\u1ea3ng 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Hi\u1ec7n ngo\u00e0i MU, Liverpool v\u00e0 Tottenham c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn Modric.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, Mourinho c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t quan t\u00e2m m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Ivan Rakitic \u2013 ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eabn \u0111ang b\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai sau khi Barcelona chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Philippe Coutinho.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>B\u1ecf MU, Mourinho s\u1ebd l\u00e0 HLV m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a PSG?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>T\u1edd Mirror nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh, HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111ang \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t ni\u1ec1m tin t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o C\u0110V MU sau khi \u00f4ng r\u0169 b\u1ecf tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m ch\u00ednh trong th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i m\u1ea5t m\u1eb7t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Sevilla v\u1eeba qua \u1edf Champions League. T\u1edd b\u00e1o n\u00e0y c\u00f2n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7t danh \u201cNg\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t\u201d c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd thay th\u1ebf ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p Unai Emery d\u1eabn d\u1eaft PSG ngay khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y k\u1ebft th\u00fac.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Sanchez kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 \u1edf MU</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Alexis Sanchez \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Old Trafford sau khi trao \u0111\u1ed5i theo chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi Henrikh Mkhitaryan trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 m\u00e0 MU v\u00e0 Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0103n v\u1edbi nhau th\u00e1ng Gi\u00eang v\u1eeba qua.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Sanchez hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u1edbi MU s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n sau 4 n\u0103m r\u01b0\u1ee1i, ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 khi anh 33 tu\u1ed5i. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 29 tu\u1ed5i ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 tr\u00ean k\u00eanh truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh Chilevision v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho La U (\u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a cha m\u00ecnh) ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Colo Colo nh\u01b0 di nguy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi cha qu\u00e1 c\u1ed1.</p><p></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>B\u1ea1o chi v\u00ec \u201cs\u1ebfu v\u01b0\u1eddn\u201d Brazil</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Sun cho hay, HLV Mourinho \u0111ang r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Anderson Talisca \u2013 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Besiktas theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb Benfica v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c MU chi \u0111\u1ebfn 35,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua anh h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tuy v\u1eady, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Besiktas c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed mua \u0111\u1ee9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil cao \u0111\u1ebfn 1,91m m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu ngay h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: Mourinho ch\u00e1n Pogba, m\u01a1 Modric ho\u1eb7c Rakitic thay th\u1ebf - 2\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-15/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-Mourinho-chan-Pogba-mo-Modric-hoac-Rakitic-thay-the-anderson-talisca-sport_-preview-1521110397-794-width660height440.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Anderson Talisca \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c MU nh\u00f2m ng\u00f3</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>\u201cDerby Manchester\u201d v\u00ec sao tr\u1ebb Dortmund</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Trang tin Read Bundesliga cho bi\u1ebft, hi\u1ec7n Man City c\u1ee7a HLV Pep Guardiola \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Julian Weigl \u2013 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c m\u1edbi 22 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng \u0111ang ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t gi\u00e0 d\u1eb7n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Dortmund. Tuy v\u1eady, MU c\u0169ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m t\u00e0i hoa n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Mourinho \u0111i\u00ean ti\u1ebft Pogba, t\u1eadu 2 SAO thay th\u1ebf</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi HLV Mourinho chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Sanchez c\u00f9ng nhi\u1ec1u \u01b0u \u00e1i v\u1ec1 l\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ed5ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea1m vi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, Paul Pogba c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t. Tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 g\u1eb7p Sevilla, Pogba v\u00e0o s\u00e2n trong hi\u1ec7p 2, kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau \u0111\u00f3 MU thua li\u1ec1n 2 b\u00e0n.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: Mourinho ch\u00e1n Pogba, m\u01a1 Modric ho\u1eb7c Rakitic thay th\u1ebf - 3\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-15/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-Mourinho-dien-tiet-Pogba-tau-2-SAO-thay-the-640mu-pogba-1521084037-939-width660height371.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">HLV Mourinho \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n thay th\u1ebf Pogba</p>\r\n\r\n<p>HLV Mourinho s\u1ebd tri\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m m\u1edbi tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i k\u1ebft th\u00fac. ESPN \u0111\u01b0a tin, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a Willian (Chelsea) v\u00e0 Verratti (PSG) v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm. \u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 hai mi\u1ebfng gh\u00e9p quan tr\u1ecdng, \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c thay th\u1ebf vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Pogba v\u00e0 gi\u00fap tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa MU c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng h\u01a1n.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>MU mua h\u00e0ng La Liga thay Darmian</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Serie A trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. HLV Mouirnho c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7. T\u1edd Tuttosport ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, MU mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Jose Gaya c\u1ee7a Valencia. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 40 tri\u1ec7u euro.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi MU, Ibrahimovic ra \u0111i</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Zlatan Ibrahimovic l\u00f9i k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ebfn M\u1ef9 l\u1ea1i 1 n\u0103m \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng MU chinh chi\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i Champions League. Trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p l\u1eaby l\u1eebng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Ibrahimovic l\u1ea1i ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng ch\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ebfn vinh quang ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, cho d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 Juventus, Inter Milan, AC Milan \u1edf Italia, Barcelona \u1edf T\u00e2y Ban Nha, PSG t\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p hay b\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 MU. Sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u201cQu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\u201d tr\u01b0\u1edbc Sevilla, t\u1edd Daily Mail ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Ibrahimovic d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd r\u1eddi MU ngay khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 6.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><div style=\"text-align: center;width: 100%;clear: both;position: relative;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"position:relative;max-width: 660px;margin: 0 auto\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: Mourinho ch\u00e1n Pogba, m\u01a1 Modric ho\u1eb7c Rakitic thay th\u1ebf - 4\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-14/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-Chinh-phuc-C1-bat-thanh-Ibrahimovic-ra-di-nintchdbpict000257411784-1482652183485-1521045801-176-width660height440.jpg\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"24h-banner-in-image\" style=\"position: absolute;display: block;overflow: hidden;width: 660px;height: 90px;color: white;bottom: 0px;left: 0px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"24h-banner-in-image-close\" style=\"top:5px;right: 5px;position: absolute;display: none;overflow: hidden;width: 22px;height: 22px;color: #ccc;font-size: large;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: Mourinho ch\u00e1n Pogba, m\u01a1 Modric ho\u1eb7c Rakitic thay th\u1ebf - 5\" onclick=\"in_image_close();\" id=\"in-image-close\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/24h_banner_image_library/in-image-close.svg\"></img>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n                \r\n            </div></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Ibrahimovic chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb n\u00f3i l\u1eddi t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t MU</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>C\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi Man City v\u00ec sao Brazil</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>T\u1edd Manchester Evening News kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, MU \u0111ang c\u1ea1nh tranh quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t v\u1edbi Man City trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Fred. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Shakhtar \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3 hai \u00f4ng l\u1edbn th\u00e0nh Manchester nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn trong n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c gia c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7. \u1ede tu\u1ed5i 25, Fred \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 5 n\u0103m ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Lindelof c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb b\u00e1n</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a MU \u1edf Champions League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 r\u1eddi Old Trafford, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 t\u00e2n binh Victor Lindelof. Trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn MU trong s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a NHM, nh\u01b0ng cho \u0111\u1ebfn nay, b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 32 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng x\u1ee9ng. Theo Daily Mail, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Benfica s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0a Lindelof tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Luke Shaw b\u1ea5t m\u00e3n \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i Luke Shaw g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 b\u1ecb HLV Jose Mourinho b\u1ecf r\u01a1i trong kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. C\u0169ng b\u1edfi v\u1eady, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a Luke Shaw t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tuy\u1ec3n Anh l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Luke Shaw \u0111ang d\u1ea7n m\u1ea5t ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi MU, \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng cho anh nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n h\u01a1n. C\u00e1i \u0111\u00edch m\u00e0 Luke Shaw nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0 Tottenham.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Mourinho mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Draxler</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Theo L\u2019Equippe, HLV Jose Mourinho mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o Julian Draxler v\u1ec1 Old Trafford trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 t\u1edbi. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng t\u1ea1i PSG. Trong th\u00e1ng 1, MU t\u1eebng li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Draxler nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. Julian Draxler kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 t\u00ednh chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai sau khi World Cup 2018 k\u1ebft th\u00fac.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"MU m\u1ea5t m\u1eb7t \u1edf c\u00fap C1: Mourinho \u201dnh\u00fat nh\u00e1t\u201d v\u1eabn v\u00f2i th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-14/1521006148-692-thumbnail.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">MU m\u1ea5t m\u1eb7t \u1edf c\u00fap C1: Mourinho \u201dnh\u00fat nh\u00e1t\u201d v\u1eabn v\u00f2i th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>MU v\u00e0 Mourinho nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft c\u1ee5c bi th\u1ea3m nh\u01b0ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u00ec th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u00fat nh\u00e1t.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"chuyen-nhuong-mu-chinh-phuc-c1-bat-thanh-ibrahimovic-ra-di-c409a945136.html","id":"431"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 N\u0103m, ng\u00e0y 15/03/2018 05:40 AM (GMT+7)","title":"G\u00f3c chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt Barca \u2013 Chelsea: Messi \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 \u201cv\u1ecb Th\u00e1nh\u201d","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-09/thumbnail/960-1520600242-943-width640height480.jpg","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3></div>\r\n\t\t <p>Ngay c\u1ea3 khi Chelsea \u0111\u1ea1t 100% phong \u0111\u1ed9, <strong>Barca </strong>v\u1eabn \u1edf c\u1eeda tr\u00ean ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n. \u0110\u1eb1ng n\u00e0y \u201cThe Blues\u201d h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n Nou Camp sau chu\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y b\u1ebft b\u00e1t, qu\u00e2n t\u00ecnh r\u1ed1i lo\u1ea1n, \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. Tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i c\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea9y h\u1ecd v\u00e0o th\u1ebf kh\u00f3, kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 co c\u1ee5m, b\u1edfi v\u1eady HLV Conte quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh x\u1ebfp Giroud \u0111\u00e1 trung phong thay v\u00ec d\u00f9ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u1ea3o v\u1edbi Hazard.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"G\u00f3c chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt Barca \u2013 Chelsea: Messi \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 \u201cv\u1ecb Th\u00e1nh\u201d - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-15/Goc-chien-thuat-Barca--Chelsea-Messi-don-gian-la-vi-Thanh-messi-1521067004-219-width660height397.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Conte ch\u01b0a k\u1ecbp toan t\u00ednh th\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Messi ch\u1ecdc th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tuy nhi\u00ean m\u1ecdi toan t\u00ednh c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng minh s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn th\u00ec Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi. Lionel Messi cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 sung m\u00e3n trong b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 \u1edf La Liga cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua, ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p ban b\u1eadt v\u1edbi Dembele v\u00e0 Suarez, c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam s\u1ef1 hoa m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 b\u0103ng l\u00ean d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u1ea1nh l\u00f9ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m x\u00e2u kim Courtois \u1edf g\u00f3c r\u1ea5t h\u1eb9p.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Conte h\u00f2 h\u00e9t c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh. Chelsea \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u00e9t. Nh\u01b0ng HLV Valverde kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i tay m\u01a1. C\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u00f4ng cho Barca ch\u01a1i ch\u1eadm r\u00e3i, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, ra s\u1ee9c \"ru ng\u1ee7\" \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed9t ng\u1ed9t t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c l\u00fac c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft. Valverde \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00e1nh \u0111i v\u00e0o v\u1ebft xe \u0111\u1ed5 nh\u01b0 6 n\u0103m v\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u nhau c\u0169ng t\u1ea1i Nou Camp m\u00e0 Barca b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chelsea b\u1ebf t\u1eafc ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn khu v\u1ef1c 16m50, Barca ch\u1ef1c ch\u1edd v\u00e0 t\u00f3m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sai l\u1ea7m \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t. Fabregas l\u00f3ng ng\u00f3ng b\u1ecb Messi c\u01b0\u1edbp b\u00f3ng ngay \u1edf gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n. Ch\u1ec9 ch\u1edd c\u00f3 th\u1ebf, s\u1ed1 10 b\u00ean ph\u00eda Barca kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua hai b\u00f3ng \u00e1o tr\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tung \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u1ecdn c\u1ed7 cho Dembele tung c\u00fa s\u00fat quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-0. Tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Chelsea xu\u1ed1ng th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 sau \u0111\u00f3.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Gi\u00e1 nh\u01b0 c\u00fa s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Alonso th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1 thay v\u00ec tr\u00fang c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc Barca th\u00ec hi v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Chelsea c\u00f2n s\u00e1ng. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e1o hi\u1ec7u cho m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y ch\u1eb3ng l\u00e0nh, \u201cThe Blues\u201d \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1eady \u1edf hi\u1ec7p 2. H\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ed1ng ch\u1ecdi v\u1edbi thi\u00ean t\u00e0i Messi v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c \u1ea5y l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 s\u1ee9c. Rudiger, Christensen ch\u1ec9 nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00e3 h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7c tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p Messi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><div style=\"text-align: center;width: 100%;clear: both;position: relative;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"position:relative;max-width: 660px;margin: 0 auto\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"G\u00f3c chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt Barca \u2013 Chelsea: Messi \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 \u201cv\u1ecb Th\u00e1nh\u201d - 2\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-15/Goc-chien-thuat-Barca--Chelsea-Messi-don-gian-la-vi-Thanh-messi3-1521067004-873-width660height485.jpg\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"24h-banner-in-image\" style=\"position: absolute;display: block;overflow: hidden;width: 660px;height: 90px;color: white;bottom: 0px;left: 0px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"24h-banner-in-image-close\" style=\"top:5px;right: 5px;position: absolute;display: none;overflow: hidden;width: 22px;height: 22px;color: #ccc;font-size: large;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"G\u00f3c chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt Barca \u2013 Chelsea: Messi \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 \u201cv\u1ecb Th\u00e1nh\u201d - 3\" onclick=\"in_image_close();\" id=\"in-image-close\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/24h_banner_image_library/in-image-close.svg\"></img>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n                \r\n            </div></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Chelsea \"ch\u1ebft\" d\u01b0\u1edbi tay thi\u00ean t\u00e0i Messi</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\u1ede t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Messi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 3 cho Barca, c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Chelsea b\u00e1m theo trong v\u00f4 v\u1ecdng c\u00f2n th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2 b\u1ecb s\u00fat b\u00f3ng qua hai ch\u00e2n. HLV Conte d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t n\u00e0o cho si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina, \u00edt nh\u1ea5t nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i khi c\u1eaft c\u1eed Kante theo k\u00e8m s\u00e1t sao v\u00e0 l\u1ebd t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u201cch\u1ebft\u201d d\u01b0\u1edbi tay Messi. &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tr\u00ean \u201c\u0111\u1ea5t M\u1eb9\u201d Nou Camp, Messi lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u201cv\u1ecb Th\u00e1nh\u201d. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea, h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u1ea5y xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ebd nh\u1ea5t trong l\u00f2ng c\u00e1c C\u0110V Barca. 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, 1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o trong 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn, Messi \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ed9t tay nh\u1ea5n ch\u00ecm Chelsea.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Messi l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap: Thi\u00ean t\u00e0i \u201dx\u1ecf h\u00e1ng\u201d, nh\u1ea5n ch\u00ecm Chelsea\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-15/1521063161-847-thumbnail.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Messi l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap: Thi\u00ean t\u00e0i \u201dx\u1ecf h\u00e1ng\u201d, nh\u1ea5n ch\u00ecm Chelsea</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>C\u1ea3 hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Messi \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m x\u1ecf h\u00e1ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"goc-chien-thuat-barca-chelsea-messi-don-gian-la-vi-thanh-c48a945151.html","id":"430"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 N\u0103m, ng\u00e0y 15/03/2018 06:35 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Barca \"ti\u00eau di\u1ec7t\" Chelsea l\u1eadp k\u00ec t\u00edch, Messi \u0111i\u1ec3m 10 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-09/thumbnail/960-1520600242-943-width640height480.jpg","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3>\r\n\t\t <p><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Barca &amp;#34;ti\u00eau di\u1ec7t&amp;#34; Chelsea l\u1eadp k\u00ec t\u00edch, Messi \u0111i\u1ec3m 10 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-15/Barca-barca-chelsea1-1521070016-175-width660height414.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">B\u00f3ng m\u1edbi l\u0103n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 ph\u00fat, Messi \u0111\u00e3 s\u00fat tung l\u01b0\u1edbi Chelsea</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Barca &amp;#34;ti\u00eau di\u1ec7t&amp;#34; Chelsea l\u1eadp k\u00ec t\u00edch, Messi \u0111i\u1ec3m 10 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o - 2\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-15/Barca-barca-chelsea2-1521070016-166-width660height429.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">C\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf g\u00f3c c\u1ef1c h\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a Messi, b\u00f3ng qua hai ch\u00e2n th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois</p><p></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Barca &amp;#34;ti\u00eau di\u1ec7t&amp;#34; Chelsea l\u1eadp k\u00ec t\u00edch, Messi \u0111i\u1ec3m 10 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o - 3\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-15/Barca-barca-chelsea4-1521070016-13-width660height394.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Messi sau \u0111\u00f3 r\u00ea d\u1eaft b\u00f3ng hai 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Chelsea r\u1ed3i ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho Dembele n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-0</p>\r\n\r\n<p><div style=\"text-align: center;width: 100%;clear: both;position: relative;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"position:relative;max-width: 660px;margin: 0 auto\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Barca &amp;#34;ti\u00eau di\u1ec7t&amp;#34; Chelsea l\u1eadp k\u00ec t\u00edch, Messi \u0111i\u1ec3m 10 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o - 4\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-15/Barca-barca-chelsea3-1521070016-496-width660height480.jpg\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"24h-banner-in-image\" style=\"position: absolute;display: block;overflow: hidden;width: 660px;height: 90px;color: white;bottom: 0px;left: 0px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"24h-banner-in-image-close\" style=\"top:5px;right: 5px;position: absolute;display: none;overflow: hidden;width: 22px;height: 22px;color: #ccc;font-size: large;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Barca &amp;#34;ti\u00eau di\u1ec7t&amp;#34; Chelsea l\u1eadp k\u00ec t\u00edch, Messi \u0111i\u1ec3m 10 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o - 5\" onclick=\"in_image_close();\" id=\"in-image-close\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/24h_banner_image_library/in-image-close.svg\"></img>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n                \r\n            </div></p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Barca &amp;#34;ti\u00eau di\u1ec7t&amp;#34; Chelsea l\u1eadp k\u00ec t\u00edch, Messi \u0111i\u1ec3m 10 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o - 6\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-15/Barca-barca-chelsea7-1521070016-101-width660height367.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Chelsea d\u1ed3n l\u00ean, t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. Alonso s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng d\u1ed9i c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Barca &amp;#34;ti\u00eau di\u1ec7t&amp;#34; Chelsea l\u1eadp k\u00ec t\u00edch, Messi \u0111i\u1ec3m 10 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o - 7\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-15/Barca-barca-chelsea10-1521070016-565-width660height394.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Sang hi\u1ec7p 2, Alonso c\u00f2n ng\u00e3 trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m, Chelsea \u0111\u00f2i penalty b\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Barca &amp;#34;ti\u00eau di\u1ec7t&amp;#34; Chelsea l\u1eadp k\u00ec t\u00edch, Messi \u0111i\u1ec3m 10 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o - 8\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-15/Barca-barca-chelsea8-1521070016-313-width660height401.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Willian v\u00e0 Hazard ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u0103ng n\u1ed5 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Barca \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Barca &amp;#34;ti\u00eau di\u1ec7t&amp;#34; Chelsea l\u1eadp k\u00ec t\u00edch, Messi \u0111i\u1ec3m 10 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o - 9\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-15/Barca-barca-chelsea9-1521070016-557-width660height445.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Barca ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn Courtois nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n kh\u1ed5 s\u1edf</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Barca &amp;#34;ti\u00eau di\u1ec7t&amp;#34; Chelsea l\u1eadp k\u00ec t\u00edch, Messi \u0111i\u1ec3m 10 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o - 10\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-15/Barca-barca-chelsea11-1521070016-775-width660height494.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">HLV Conte h\u1ebft tr\u1eadn, kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i v\u00ec qu\u00e1 n\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c Messi n\u00ean kh\u00e1 t\u01b0\u01a1i d\u00f9 Chelsea b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Barca &amp;#34;ti\u00eau di\u1ec7t&amp;#34; Chelsea l\u1eadp k\u00ec t\u00edch, Messi \u0111i\u1ec3m 10 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o - 11\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-15/Barca-barca1-1521070405-811-width660height458.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-style: italic; text-align: left;\">Trong khi Barca c\u00f3 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 11 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 chu\u1ed7i d\u00e0i nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. Messi theo ch\u1ea5m \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a trang Whoscored nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec3m 10 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Messi c\u00e1n m\u1ed1c 100 b\u00e0n C\u00fap C1: Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u201dc\u00f4 \u0111\u01a1n\u201d\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-15/1521067616-145-thumbnail.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Messi c\u00e1n m\u1ed1c 100 b\u00e0n C\u00fap C1: Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u201dc\u00f4 \u0111\u01a1n\u201d</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>Messi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ee9 2 \u0111\u1ea1t 100 b\u00e0n \u1edf Champions League/C\u00fap C1 sau Ronaldo.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"barca-tieu-diet-chelsea-lap-ki-tich-messi-diem-10-hoan-hao-c48a945155.html","id":"429"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 N\u0103m, ng\u00e0y 15/03/2018 06:35 AM (GMT+7)","title":"B\u1ed1c th\u0103m t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft C1: R\u00f2 r\u1ec9 \u00e2m m\u01b0u s\u1ed1c, Si\u00eau kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n Barca - Real","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-09/thumbnail/960-1520600242-943-width640height480.jpg","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3>\r\n\t\t <p>8 chi\u1ebfc v\u00e9 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 ch\u1ee7. Barcelona tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t, sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Chelsea v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-0 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Nou Camp. Do v\u1eady, 8 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft bao g\u1ed3m \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Real Madrid, c\u00e1c \u00f4ng l\u1edbn <strong>Barcelona</strong>, Juventus, Bayern Munich, Liverpool, Man City c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c ch\u00fa ng\u1ef1a \u00f4 AS Roma v\u00e0 Sevilla.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"B\u1ed1c th\u0103m t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft C1: R\u00f2 r\u1ec9 \u00e2m m\u01b0u s\u1ed1c, Si\u00eau kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n Barca - Real - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-15/Boc-tham-tu-ket-C1-Ro-ri-am-muu-soc-Sieu-kinh-dien-Barca---Real-4a32cbac00000578-5501573-image-a-118_1521061937581-1521070021-707-width660height382.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Messi gi\u00fap Barca gi\u00e0nh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ng\u00e0y mai - l\u00fac 18h th\u1ee9 S\u00e1u (gi\u1edd VN), 16/3 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m ph\u00e2n c\u1eb7p t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i Nyon, Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9. Nh\u1eefng l\u00e1 phi\u1ebfu s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 th\u00e0nh b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. V\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u mong ng\u00f3ng l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m do UEFA t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng, ngay sau th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m <em>Barcelona</em> h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Chelsea, c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng tin r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tung h\u00ea tr\u00ean c\u00e1c m\u1eb7t b\u00e1o. Theo \u0111\u00f3, UEFA \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u201c\u00e2m m\u01b0u\u201d \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chi ph\u1ed1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i danh gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t l\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ecba gi\u00e0. N\u00ean nh\u1edb r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e3 4 n\u0103m li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb 2014 \u0111\u1ebfn nay, Champions League tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f2 - Real 3 l\u1ea7n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, l\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Barcelona.</p><p></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Do v\u1eady, n\u1ebfu Barcelona v\u00e0 Real tr\u00e1nh nhau \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd bi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Th\u1ebf n\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng UEFA t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i b\u1edbt m\u1ed9t trong hai \u00f4ng l\u1edbn x\u1ee9 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f2.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Theo Sport Mediaset c\u1ee7a Italia, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m ph\u00e2n c\u1eb7p t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League r\u00f2 r\u1ec9 ngay t\u1eeb b\u00e2y gi\u1edd. Theo \u0111\u00f3, s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n gi\u1eefa <u>Barcelona</u> v\u00e0 Real Madrid. 3 c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn derby n\u1eefa gi\u1eefa ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia l\u00e0 Juventus v\u00e0 AS Roma; Man City g\u1eb7p kh\u1eafc tinh v\u1eeba \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i MU l\u00e0 Sevilla, trong khi Liverpool ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u00f4ng l\u1edbn Bayern Munich.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"B\u1ed1c th\u0103m t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft C1: R\u00f2 r\u1ec9 \u00e2m m\u01b0u s\u1ed1c, Si\u00eau kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n Barca - Real - 2\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-15/Boc-tham-tu-ket-C1-Ro-ri-am-muu-soc-Sieu-kinh-dien-Barca---Real-c_29_articolo_1202508_lstparagrafi_paragrafo_0_upi-1521070052-915-width660height338.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">R\u00f2 r\u1ec9 th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 Si\u00eau kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League</p>\r\n\r\n<p>N\u1ebfu \u00e2m m\u01b0u m\u00e0 Sport Mediaset ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u00fang s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c - r\u1eb1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y mai c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n Real - Barca, th\u00ec \u0111\u00e2y qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u00ea b\u1ed1i m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a UEFA. Ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ed1 r\u1eb1ng UEFA \u0111ang \u201cn\u00e2ng \u0111\u1ee1\u201d ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh - \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Man City, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i th\u00f4ng qua b\u00e0n tay c\u1ee7a 5 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh h\u1ea1 b\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3 MU, Chelsea v\u00e0 Tottenham c\u00f9ng \u201cr\u1edbt \u0111\u00e0i\u201d, ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a UEFA v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n s\u00f3t l\u1ea1i Man City m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. N\u1ebfu n\u1eeda xanh th\u00e0nh Manchester ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p Sevilla - \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, th\u00ec \u0111\u00e2y qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f3n h\u1eddi v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Barca v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft: Valverde n\u1ed5 to, khen Messi nh\u01b0 \u201cTh\u00e1nh s\u1ed1ng\u201d\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-15/640x480-1521068583-310-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Barca v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft: Valverde n\u1ed5 to, khen Messi nh\u01b0 \u201cTh\u00e1nh s\u1ed1ng\u201d</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>Barcelona \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh Chelsea.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"boc-tham-tu-ket-c1-ro-ri-am-muu-soc-sieu-kinh-dien-barca-real-c48a945156.html","id":"428"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 N\u0103m, ng\u00e0y 15/03/2018 05:22 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Barcelona - Chelsea: Si\u00eau sao nh\u1ea3y m\u00faa, v\u1eadn may ngo\u1ea3nh m\u1eb7t","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-09/thumbnail/960-1520600242-943-width640height480.jpg","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3>\r\n\t\t <p>V\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 1-1 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, <strong>Barcelona </strong>nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn h\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Chelsea. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Nou Camp d\u1ed3n \u00e9p ngay sau ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i khai cu\u1ed9c, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i mau ch\u00f3ng c\u00f3 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ch\u1ec9 sau 3 ph\u00fat. M\u1ed9t pha t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a Messi, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Chelsea cho\u00e1ng v\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i sau \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Suarez, Messi x\u00e2u kim th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Courtois m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Barcelona - Chelsea: Si\u00eau sao nh\u1ea3y m\u00faa, v\u1eadn may ngo\u1ea3nh m\u1eb7t - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-15/Ket-qua-bong-da-Barcelona---Chelsea-Sieu-sao-choi-sang-loi-the-cuc-lon-1521059789505_lc_galleryimage_barcelona_s_samuel_u-1521060412-346-width660height446.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">\u0110\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Barca - Chelsea di\u1ec5n ra c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng, quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, Barcelona v\u1eabn l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Chelsea sau khi v\u1ee1 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch, bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea9y cao \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh h\u00f2ng t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n g\u1ee1. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y London l\u1ed9 ra nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu ch\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Ph\u00fat 20, Cesc Fabregas trong ng\u00e0y tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Nou Camp, c\u00f3 pha m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7. Messi c\u01b0\u1edbp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00f3ng, t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c c\u1ef1c nhanh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tung \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o s\u1eafc l\u1eb9m \u0111\u1ec3 Dembele gia t\u0103ng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t. <em>Barcelona </em>d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2 b\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 sau 20 ph\u00fat.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>B\u00e0n thua th\u1ee9 hai nh\u01b0 khi\u1ebfn Chelsea b\u1eebng t\u1ec9nh. H\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o ra. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Alonso, Kante, Giroud hay Willian \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng \u0111em l\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Ph\u00fat 45, v\u1eadn may c\u00f2n ngo\u1ea3nh m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng \u0111i tr\u00fang c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a Alonso. 2-0 l\u00e0 t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9, Chelsea t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t h\u00f2ng mau ch\u00f3ng t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n r\u00fat ng\u1eafn c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee9 l\u0169 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u00f4i qua m\u0169i gi\u00e0y c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u00e1o tr\u1eafng. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Barcelona d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Ernesto Valverde r\u1ea5t gi\u1ecfi trong kh\u00e2u k\u1ebft li\u1ec5u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Ph\u00fat 63, m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa l\u00e0 thi\u00ean t\u00e0i Messi ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi pha b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1c qua to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi x\u00e2u kim Courtois th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa. Barcelona d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea 3-0.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\u0110\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u xem nh\u01b0 an b\u00e0i. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Chelsea c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea9y cao t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00eam n\u1eefa. Ngay c\u1ea3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng danh d\u1ef1, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1 Alonso \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t tr\u00fang c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc th\u00ec \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 2, Rudiger \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng tr\u00fang x\u00e0 ngang. V\u1eadn may ngo\u1ea3nh m\u1eb7t, Chelsea b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i c\u00f2n <u>Barcelona </u>ghi t\u00ean m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>T\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai: <u>Barcelona 3-0 Chelsea</u></strong>&nbsp;(H1: 2-0)</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-style: italic;\">* Barcelona gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-1, l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ghi b\u00e0n:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Barcelona: Messi 3' - 63', Dembele 20'</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Barcelona: Ter Stegen \u2013 Roberto, Pique, Umtiti, Alba \u2013 Busquet, Rakitic, Iniesta \u2013 Dembele, Suarez, Messi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chelsea: Courtois \u2013 Rudiger, Christensen, Azpilicueta \u2013 Alonso, Fabregas, Kante, Moses \u2013 Hazard, Giroud, Willian.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"1\" class=\"no-borders\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; max-width: 500px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; f