lay:none\"></div><div id=\"zplayer_cc6dc1_ga_doi_tac\" style=\"display:none\"></div></div><!-- end_media_player \r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-style: italic;\">*Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, m\u1eddi qu\u00fd v\u1ecb ch\u00fa \u00fd theo d\u00f5i!</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Arsenal</strong> \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u01a1n kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng th\u1eadt ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c v\u00e0 c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n Milan tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Wenger thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp 4 tr\u1eadn. H\u1ecd b\u1ecb Man City gi\u1eadt m\u1ea5t ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch League Cup, thua ti\u1ebfp 0-3 sau \u0111\u00f3 1 tu\u1ea7n v\u00e0 t\u1ed9t c\u00f9ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00e2n binh Brighton.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Arsenal \u2013 AC Milan: \u201cPh\u00e1o\u201d quy\u1ebft n\u1ed5 to, &amp;#34;r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t&amp;#34; Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh - 2\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-15/Nhan-dinh-bong-da-Arsenal--AC-Milan-Phao-quyet-no-to-arsenal-2-1521081098-913-width660height444.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng Milan \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eadp tan kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng</p><p></p>\r\n\r\n<p>\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n cho r\u1eb1ng HLV Wenger s\u1ebd bay gh\u1ebf n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Arsenal tr\u1eafng tay r\u1eddi San Siro gi\u1eefa tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i, b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a \u201cGi\u00e1o s\u01b0\u201d t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p m\u1ed9t Milan non n\u1edbt c\u1ee7a Gattuso. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 c\u00f9ng th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o \u0111\u00e3 k\u00e9o \u201cPh\u00e1o th\u1ee7\u201d t\u1eeb \u0111\u00e1y v\u1ef1c s\u00e2u l\u00ean m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea5t.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ngu\u1ed3n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng t\u1eeb San Siro \u0111\u00e3 lan t\u1ecfa v\u1ec1 Premier League. Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua, Arsenal th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng Watford, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu 3 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Emirates. \u0110\u00e2y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0 c\u00fa h\u00edch tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 Arsenal n\u1ed1i d\u00e0i m\u1ea1ch tr\u1eadn th\u0103ng hoa.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>T\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u AC Milan \u0111\u00eam nay, HLV Wenger c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn. Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin \u201cPh\u00e1o th\u1ee7\u201d s\u1ebd bung s\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1 quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t. Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u Premier League b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Leicester b\u1eadn thi \u0111\u1ea5u FA Cup. Sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 qu\u00e3ng ngh\u1ec9 d\u00e0i nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho \u0111\u1ee3t giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>V\u00ec th\u1ebf Arsenal mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng gi\u00f2n gi\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng. <em>HLV Wenger</em> v\u1eabn s\u1ebd tung ra b\u1ed9 khung l\u00e0m n\u00ean chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i. Tam t\u1ea5u&nbsp;Welbeck, Ozil, Mkhitaryan l\u0129nh x\u01b0\u1edbng h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. Wilshere v\u00e0 Ramsey s\u1eafm vai \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 khu trung tuy\u1ebfn trong khi Xhaka nh\u1eadn nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u201cm\u00e1y qu\u00e9t\u201d.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><div style=\"text-align: center;width: 100%;clear: both;position: relative;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"position:relative;max-width: 660px;margin: 0 auto\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Arsenal \u2013 AC Milan: \u201cPh\u00e1o\u201d quy\u1ebft n\u1ed5 to, &amp;#34;r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t&amp;#34; Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh - 3\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-15/Nhan-dinh-bong-da-Arsenal--AC-Milan-Phao-quyet-no-to-arsenal-milan-1521081098-639-width660height440.jpg\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"24h-banner-in-image\" style=\"position: absolute;display: block;overflow: hidden;width: 660px;height: 90px;color: white;bottom: 0px;left: 0px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"24h-banner-in-image-close\" style=\"top:5px;right: 5px;position: absolute;display: none;overflow: hidden;width: 22px;height: 22px;color: #ccc;font-size: large;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Arsenal \u2013 AC Milan: \u201cPh\u00e1o\u201d quy\u1ebft n\u1ed5 to, &amp;#34;r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t&amp;#34; Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh - 4\" onclick=\"in_image_close();\" id=\"in-image-close\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/24h_banner_image_library/in-image-close.svg\"></img>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n                \r\n            </div></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Wenger s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \"n\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u00e2n\" tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0</p>\r\n\r\n<p>AC Milan c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t. V\u1edbi c\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n thua 2 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 c\u00e1 t\u00ednh m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd c\u1ee7a HLV Gattuso, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Serie A s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea7n ng\u1ea1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i Emirates. AC Milan \u1ea5p \u1ee7 tham v\u1ecdng g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c ho\u1eb7c c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i trong th\u1ebf ng\u1ea9ng cao \u0111\u1ea7u.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>AC Milan kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t khi h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9. Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea t\u1ea1i c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u cho th\u1ea5y \u201cRossoneri\u201d ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 thua \u0111\u1ebfn 9 tr\u1eadn sau 16 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Anh. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 <u>Arsenal</u> l\u1ea1i ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Serie A t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 v\u1edbi 9 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng sau 15&nbsp;l\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n (thua 2).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>D\u1ef0 \u0110O\u00c1N:</strong> <u>Arsenal 2-0 AC Milan</u></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Arsenal (4-2-3-1): </strong>Ospina; Bellerin, Mustafi, Koscielny, Monreal; Xhaka, Ramsey; Wilshere, Mkhitaryan, Ozil; Welbeck</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>AC Milan (4-3-3):</strong> Donnarumma; Calabria, Bonucci, Romagnoli, Rodriguez; Biglia, Kessie, Bonaventura; Suso, Calhanoglu, Cutrone</p>\r\n\r\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"3\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border:1px solid #bbb;background-color:#DEF1C8;margin:5px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" width=\"500\">\r\n\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:justify\" valign=\"top\">\r\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Th\u00f4ng tin l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t<p>Arsenal: Cazorla, Lacazette ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng; Aubameyang kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u.</p>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t<p>AC Milan: Conte v\u00e0 Abate ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.</p>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Th\u00f4ng tin b\u00ean l\u1ec1:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t<p>Arsenal th\u1eafng 9 h\u00f2a 4 thua 2 khi ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Italia \u1edf C\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.</p>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t<p>AC Milan ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 1 thua 9 sau 16 l\u1ea7n l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i Anh \u1edf C\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.</p>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t<p>Arsenal ch\u1ec9 thua 1 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i Europa League tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 (th\u1eafng 6 h\u00f2a 2).</p>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t<p>L\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Arsenal (2012), AC Milan thua 0-3.</p>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t<p>Arsenal \u0111ang h\u1ed3i sinh v\u1edbi 2 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.</p>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t<p>Arsenal l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Premier League \u1edf&nbsp;Europa League.</p>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Arsenal - Watford: Penalty h\u1ecfng \u0103n, \u201dph\u00e1o n\u1ed5\u201d t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-11/a4-1520778905-237-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Arsenal - Watford: Penalty h\u1ecfng \u0103n, \u201dph\u00e1o n\u1ed5\u201d t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>Arsenal ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f4ng n\u1ea3y l\u1eeda v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Emirates.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"nhan-dinh-bong-da-arsenal-ac-milan-phao-quyet-no-to-rua-mat-ngoai-hang-anh-c48a945193.html","id":"425"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 N\u0103m, ng\u00e0y 15/03/2018 00:01 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 15/3: Wenger tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 r\u1eddi Arsenal cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y?","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-09/thumbnail/960-1520600242-943-width640height480.jpg","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Wenger tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 r\u1eddi Arsenal cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y? </strong>C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Arsenal, Charlie Nicholas - ng\u01b0\u1eddi hi\u1ec7n l\u00e0m ngh\u1ec1 b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn vi\u00ean b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 d\u1ef1 c\u1ea3m r\u1eb1ng HLV Wenger s\u1ebd ra th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng quan tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 S\u00e1u t\u1edbi. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c Arsenal sau khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i. Nh\u01b0ng the Nicholas, Gi\u00e1o s\u01b0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi h\u1eb3n Emirates m\u00e0 v\u1eabn \u1edf l\u1ea1i l\u00e0m trong gi\u1edbi th\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea7ng v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 15/3: Wenger tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 r\u1eddi Arsenal cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y? - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-14/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-15-3-Wenger-tuyen-bo-roi-Arsenal-cuoi-tuan-nay-wenger-1521044154-63-width660height424.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Gi\u1eefa tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Arsenal s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 g\u1eb7p AC Milan \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 Europa League (l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i th\u1eafng 2-0).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>\u0110\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t Si\u00eau gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00e2u \u00c2u: </strong>Nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi M\u1ef9, Stephen Ross cho hay, \u00f4ng \u0111ang \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi mang t\u00ean European Super League (Si\u00eau gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00e2u \u00c2u) v\u1edbi 24 CLB tham gia, thay th\u1ebf cho Champions League. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 CLB kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 lu\u1eadt c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh (FFP).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Tottenham x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 c\u1ee7a Harry Kane:</strong> Trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua (14/3), Tottenham ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh ki\u1ec3m tra l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00e2y ch\u1eb1ng m\u1eaft c\u00e1 ch\u00e2n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Harry Kane. Tin vui cho C\u0110V \"G\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng\" khi m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec1u ti\u1ebfn tri\u1ec3n t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau 6 tu\u1ea7n n\u1eefa.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Lukaku gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch v\u1ee5 ch\u00ea tr\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i:</strong> Sau tr\u1eadn thua Sevilla 1-2 khi\u1ebfn MU b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi C\u00fap C1, trong cu\u1ed9c tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n tr\u00ean BT Sport, Lukaku \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ea tr\u00e1ch m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u201c\u0111\u00e1 nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ea9n tr\u1ed1n\u201d \u1edf Old Trafford. Ngo\u00e0i ra ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn, MU ch\u01a1i t\u1ed3i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. Nh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3, anh \u0111\u00ednh ch\u00ednh tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i Instagram kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u1edf ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Tr\u00f2 c\u0169 ca ng\u1ee3i Mourinho:</strong> C\u1ef1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i Brazil, Maicon n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Inter m\u00f9a 2009/10 tr\u00ean Gazzetta dello Sport: \"Mancini l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng l\u1ea1i Inter nh\u01b0ng Mourinho l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ra \u0111\u00f2n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 th\u1eadt ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o. Ch\u0103c ch\u1eafn \u00f4ng \u1ea5y l\u00e0 hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean gi\u1ecfi nh\u1ea5t t\u00f4i t\u1eebng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c\".</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Neymar ti\u1ebfn c\u1eed t\u00e2n binh cho PSG: </strong>Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i PSG. Theo \u0111\u00f3, anh \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb PSG chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 cho m\u00ecnh 2 ng\u00f4i sao: \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Casemiro c\u1ee7a Real Madrid v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Ter Stegen c\u1ee7a Barcelona. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 hai v\u1ecb tr\u00ed y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u1edf m\u00f9a n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"MU thua s\u1ed1c: Sanchez b\u1ecb c\u1ea3 Arsenal gh\u00e9t, MU l\u1ee1 mua \u201ctr\u00f9m ph\u00e1 team\u201d?\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-14/reports-emerge-of-how-much-arsenal-dressing-room-hated-alexis-sanchez-640-1521023078-161-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">MU thua s\u1ed1c: Sanchez b\u1ecb c\u1ea3 Arsenal gh\u00e9t, MU l\u1ee1 mua \u201ctr\u00f9m ph\u00e1 team\u201d?</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>Nh\u1eefng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng hay v\u1ec1 Alexis Sanchez v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o MU.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-15-3-wenger-tuyen-bo-roi-arsenal-cuoi-tuan-nay-c409a945134.html","id":"424"}]}